fields.name: Royal Blood (Passive):
fields.value:
During elections for a new King, votes for you count twice.
- Passive kept on class change.

fields.name: Bat Eyelashes (Night):
fields.value:
Entrance target player with your eyes into revealing their ~~class~~ role type.
- Can't target King

fields.name: Dark Wisp (Night, 2 Uses):
fields.value: Uncage a dark wisp, making the Unseen appear not suspicious tonight.
